1. *Sećam* se da sam juče zaboravio da kupim hleb. (I remember that I forgot to buy bread yesterday.)
2. Ana *se seća* kako su se njena deca igrala u parku. (Ana remembers how her children played in the park.)
3. Nisam siguran da li *sećanje* na tu noć uopšte želim da oživljavam. (I'm not sure if I want to revive the memory of that night at all.)
4. On *seća* na tebe kada god čuje pesmu koju si volela. (He remembers you every time he hears the song you loved.)
5. Da li se *sećate* kako smo se sreli pre pet godina? (Do you remember how we met five years ago?)
6. Nakon pada s bicikla, Marko se *sećao* samo parčića nesreće. (After falling off his bike, Marko only remembered bits of the accident.)
7. *Sećaš li se* da smo zakazali sastanak sa klijentima u petak ujutru? (Do you remember that we scheduled a meeting with clients on Friday morning?)
8. Kada smo bili mali, moj brat i ja smo *sećanja* stvarali praveći kućice od kartona. (When we were kids, my brother and I created memories by making cardboard houses.)
9. Ona *sećanja* su mi obeležila detinjstvo i uvek ću ih čuvati. (Those memories of hers have marked my childhood and I will always cherish them.)
10. *Sećate se* kako smo se smejali našim glupostima na prošlom putovanju? (Do you remember how we laughed at our foolishness on the last trip?)